  "3022260": {
    "name": "Beyond The Board Demo",
    "steam_appid": 3022260,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3022260/extras/9274bd4c4061e612f3672654281d6a3b.poster.avif?t=1760038009\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3022260/extras/9274bd4c4061e612f3672654281d6a3b.webm?t=1760038009\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3022260/extras/9274bd4c4061e612f3672654281d6a3b.mp4?t=1760038009\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>这（不是）一款象棋游戏</strong> <br> <br>这是一款单人解谜游戏，将传统国际象棋转化为一场极简而沉浸的旅程。每一步棋，都是深入“棋盘之外”世界的一步；在那里，变换的方格与谜题揭示了游戏根基中的隐藏裂痕.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> </strong><br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3022260/extras/b661d6b7c98cca436a827615a8c1dde7.poster.avif?t=1760038009\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3022260/extras/b661d6b7c98cca436a827615a8c1dde7.webm?t=1760038009\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3022260/extras/b661d6b7c98cca436a827615a8c1dde7.mp4?t=1760038009\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>故事</strong><br>在一场棋赛中，一道神秘的闪电打断了游戏，粉碎了棋盘，将棋子卷入未知的深渊。你只剩下一只战车，必须穿越这个全新的三维象棋世界，追逐敌方国王，寻找答案，并找回失散的伙伴。  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3022260/extras/cbc9f27051800f1563c1c63516e045b2.poster.avif?t=1760038009\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3022260/extras/cbc9f27051800f1563c1c63516e045b2.webm?t=1760038009\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3022260/extras/cbc9f27051800f1563c1c63516e045b2.mp4?t=1760038009\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong><br>解谜机制</strong> <br> <br>在这场象棋之旅中，每个关卡都融合了经典将死策略，并加入了新的规则与条件，迫使玩家跳出常规思维。游戏还包含触发移动方块的开关，带来更复杂、更动态的关卡设计，使环境更加鲜活。  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong></strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3022260/extras/c2231ca826853b22ada2459171664afd.poster.avif?t=1760038009\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3022260/extras/c2231ca826853b22ada2459171664afd.webm?t=1760038009\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3022260/extras/c2231ca826853b22ada2459171664afd.mp4?t=1760038009\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong><br>敌人</strong> <br> <br>在这个世界中，你将面对带有独特诅咒的敌方棋子。要打败它们，你必须理解它们的行为模式并设法反制。在每个象棋王国的尽头，都有一枚强大的Boss棋子等待着你。征服这些艰难的挑战后，你将解锁更多关于棋盘之外世界的秘密。  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong></strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3022260/extras/325b4179cdfac615b61e2509ca25e78c.poster.avif?t=1760038009\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3022260/extras/325b4179cdfac615b61e2509ca25e78c.webm?t=1760038009\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3022260/extras/325b4179cdfac615b61e2509ca25e78c.mp4?t=1760038009\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong><br>可重玩性</strong> <br> <br>我们的关卡设计包含隐藏路径，类似银河战士恶魔城（Metroidvania）类游戏。随着你解锁特定棋子并扩展队伍，这些路径将逐渐开放。你还可以通过关卡选择器，用不同组合的棋子重玩旧关卡，发现新的路线和谜题解法。  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong></strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3022260/extras/e8ec645603e533393d0de7cf21896e46.poster.avif?t=1760038009\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3022260/extras/e8ec645603e533393d0de7cf21896e46.webm?t=1760038009\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3022260/extras/e8ec645603e533393d0de7cf21896e46.mp4?t=1760038009\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong><br>接下来是什么？ </strong><br> <br>这个尚在开发中的项目还有更多精彩内容即将登场！请将游戏加入愿望单并支持我们，让这个变幻棋盘与烧脑谜题构成的世界真正活起来！</p>",
